# AgentFoundry UI

AgentFoundry UI is the shared frontend for Foundry-style apps.

This repo owns:

- the React/Vite source for the shared app UI
- a packaged static build under `src/agent_foundry_ui/dist`
- a tiny Python helper for mounting that build into a FastAPI app

## Install

```bash
npm install
```

## Develop The Shared UI

```bash
VITE_API_BASE=http://127.0.0.1:8000 npm run dev -- --host 127.0.0.1 --port 3000
```

## Build The Packaged UI

```bash
npm run build
```

This writes the production bundle into `src/agent_foundry_ui/dist`, which is the artifact consumed by app repos.

## Mount In An App

```python
from agent_foundry.server import create_app
from agent_foundry_ui import mount_ui

app = create_app(config)
mount_ui(app)
```
